      <title>FTC 称高通因反垄断问题终止 Autotalks 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/qualcomm-ends-autotalks-deal-over-antitrust-concerns-ftc-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦贸易委员会周一在一份声明中表示，在监管机构表达反垄断担忧后，高通公司放弃了收购半导体公司 Autotalks Ltd. 的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/qualcomm-ends-autotalks-deal-over-antitrust-concerns-ftc-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:27:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lightspeed 首席执行官 Dasilva 表示公司对私有化持“开放态度”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/lightspeed-ceo-dasilva-says-company-is-open-to-going-private</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大 Lightspeed Commerce Inc. 的负责人表示，最近有关私募股权收购支付公司 Nuvei Corp. 的讨论让他思考自己的公司是否也应该这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/lightspeed-ceo-dasilva-says-company-is-open-to-going-private</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:27:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌拉圭Nearsure计划员工激增50%，2024年登陆欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/uruguay-s-nearsure-plans-50-staff-surge-europe-landing-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌拉圭IT服务公司Nearsure高管表示，今年计划将员工数量增加50%，达到约850人，以满足美国企业客户不断增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/uruguay-s-nearsure-plans-50-staff-surge-europe-landing-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 12:36:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>环保组织提出要求停止道达尔南非石油钻探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/groups-file-court-bid-to-halt-total-s-south-africa-oil-drilling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环保组织向法院提起诉讼，要求阻止 TotalEnergies SE 在南非的石油勘探活动，这是支持消除化石燃料使用的活动人士与在该地区运营的能源公司之间的最新争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/groups-file-court-bid-to-halt-total-s-south-africa-oil-drilling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 12:15:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱立信将在瑞典裁员 1,200 人以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/ericsson-to-cut-1-200-jobs-in-sweden-to-cope-with-lower-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的 5G 网络设备提供商之一爱立信表示，由于移动提供商的销售额下降，该公司将在瑞典裁员 1,200 人，以降低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/ericsson-to-cut-1-200-jobs-in-sweden-to-cope-with-lower-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 12:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔、AMD 因报告中国限制使用美国芯片而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/intel-amd-fall-on-report-china-to-limit-use-of-foreign-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司和超微半导体公司的股价周一下跌，此前有报道称中国采取了新的指导方针，限制在政府计算机中使用美国制造的微处理器和服务器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/intel-amd-fall-on-report-china-to-limit-use-of-foreign-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对苹果、谷歌、Meta 进行新数字法测试调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟对苹果公司、Alphabet公司旗下谷歌和Meta Platforms公司是否遵守限制大型科技公司权力的严格新法律展开全面调查，它们面临着潜在巨额罚款的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
